@desc The screen resolution may be set incorrectly.

This can happen because the display resolution that you have set it is not
the right one for your screen.

To solve this, open the $Activities; overview and start typing $gui(Displays).
Click on $gui(Displays) to open the panel. Try some of the $gui(Resolution)
options and set the one that makes the screen look better.

